title: The 2020 NFL Draft is here! Final Tua Tagavailoa predictions, biggest draft day questions (Football 4/23)
description:
We made it. After months of anticipation, it's finally draft day and the Pick Six Superfriends are here to get you fully prepared with those last-minute burning questions. Will Brinson, Ryan Wilson, John Breech and Sean Wagner-McGough give their final predictions on when and where Tua Tagovailoa will land (4:00). The guys also issue their biggest remaining questions like will the draft be hacked and which teams will draft their quarterbacks of the future (18:50)? Lastly, your mailbag questions are answered courtesy of the Pick Six podcast Facebook group and 5-star reviews on Apple Podcasts (38:30).

'Pick Six' is available on Apple Podcasts, Spotify, Stitcher, Google Podcasts, Castbox, Bullhorn and wherever else you listen to podcasts.
